  "texts": [
    "Using only question similarity for retrieving demonstrations (-w/o pattern similarity) results in a performance drop on Spider but less so on BIRD.",
    "This could be because Spider has less question variety than BIRD, making it easier to group similar text-to-SQL samples based on their patterns.",
    "Then, when replacing our demonstration retrieval strategy with a purely random selection (-w/o demonstration retriever), performance decreases in most scenarios.Schema Filter and Value Retriever.",
    "We explore the effects of the schema filter and value retriever on performance.",
    "Without the schema filter, there's both a drop in performance and a slower generation speed due to longer input sequences."
